      {
       "data": " Out[124]= -h\\,u\\,\\left(z\\left(1\\right)\\,\\mathrm{ee}\\left(S1,S2\\right)\\left(1,1\\right)+z\\left(2\\right)\\,\\mathrm{ee}\\left(S1,S2\\right)\\left(2,2\\right)+z\\left(3\\right)\\,\\mathrm{ee}\\left(S1,S2\\right)\\left(3,3\\right)\\right)+u^2\\,\\left(z\\left(1\\right)+z\\left(2\\right)+z\\left(3\\right)\\right)-u\\,\\left(z\\left(1\\right)+z\\left(2\\right)+z\\left(3\\right)\\right)\\,\\left(\\theta1+\\theta2\\right)",
